sequenceDiagram
    participant W_A as Workload A (Web)
    participant VEN_A as VEN Agent A
    participant PCE as PCE (The Brain)
    participant VEN_B as VEN Agent B
    participant W_B as Workload B (DB)

    Note over W_A, W_B: Initial Traffic Request
    W_A->>VEN_A: Request Connection
    VEN_A->>PCE: Query Policy for DB Access
    PCE-->>VEN_A: Apply "Allow" Rule
    VEN_A->>VEN_B: Encrypted Data Flow
    VEN_B->>W_B: Deliver Request